{"id":268039,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-杭州上访维权者沈志华被押回当地后受警/","date":"2012-12-13T00:16:20Z","modified":"2012-12-13T00:16:20Z","title":"维权网 | 杭州上访维权者沈志华被押回当地后受警方审讯","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张吉安报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日早上</span><span>，浙江安吉访民沈志华和本县的王群兰、殷根娣到联合国人权驻华机构，遭警察阻挡，要送她们去久敬庄，沈志华逃脱，但在回转的路上经过美国大使馆时被武警拦住，扭送到北京朝阳区麦子店派出所，下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>时送往马家楼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>下午，沈志华被安吉县警方押回老家后，关在递铺镇派出所，有六个警察审她，现在（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>分</span><span>）正在审讯，沈志华拒绝回答任何问题。警察说她到美国大使馆是犯了叛国罪，她估计又要拘留了，可能面临劳教或判刑。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>本网将密切关注沈志华上访申诉的权利及人身自由权。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>沈志华的电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13567270029</span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-8530316459897152018?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author